      "FakeOutDeathAMurasakiRegular": {
        "id": "FakeOutDeathAMurasakiRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Red Herring",
          "description": "The user becomes a Guardian. For any enemy attack that would hit 1 or 2 other allies, 1 of the hits is instead redirected to this unit. This unit will not redirect skills that don't deal damage.\n\nAfter this skill is used, whenever the user is hit by an attack and is defeated or survives with 25% or less of max HP until after the end of the turn:\n- They are sacrificed if they were not defeated.\n- A copy of the user is added to next in line of ally reinforcements. The copy's Limit Breaks, Awakenings, Boosts, Potential, Mastery, Weapon and Accessory will match the user.\n- All allies become Enraged and have their current TU reduced by 100. This will overwrite the effects of other Enrage skills on those allies. Enraged units have their Attack increased to 1.5x until the end of their next turn.\n\nThese effects won't trigger if defeated by the burn status effect.\n\nUnlocked the first time an ally on the battlefield is defeated or sacrificed by any source while this unit is on the battlefield or if this unit is on the battlefield at the very start of the battle. This skill is locked again if the user leaves the battlefield. This skill can only be used once each time this unit is on the battlefield.",
          "selected": "Becomes Guardian"
